# Keep documentation in sync with code

When you change **user-visible behavior**, **CLI/TUI contracts**, **data loading**, **pixi tasks**, or **project layout**, update documentation in the **same change** (do not defer).

## Doc tree

**Hub:** [docs/index.md](../docs/index.md)

| Area | Update when you change… |
|------|-------------------------|
| [docs/principles.md](../docs/principles.md) | Goals, non-goals, UX values |
| [docs/architecture.md](../docs/architecture.md) | Crates, module map, shared model |
| [docs/getting-started.md](../docs/getting-started.md) | Binaries, entry points, setup |
| [docs/features/cli.md](../docs/features/cli.md) | CLI commands, filter syntax |
| [docs/features/tui.md](../docs/features/tui.md) | TUI layout, keys, mouse (`csv-utils/src/tui/app.rs`) |
| [docs/features/web.md](../docs/features/web.md) | Web UI, API, theme |
| [docs/reference/data-loading.md](../docs/reference/data-loading.md) | Preview APIs, threading |
| [docs/reference/csv-parsing.md](../docs/reference/csv-parsing.md) | `split_row`, column types, cells |
| [docs/reference/limitations.md](../docs/reference/limitations.md) | Known constraints |
| [docs/development/build.md](../docs/development/build.md) | Pixi tasks, conda recipe |
| [docs/test-data-generation.md](../docs/test-data-generation.md) | `scripts/generate_test_data.py` |
| [README.md](../README.md) | Quick start, task examples |

[docs/DESIGN.md](../docs/DESIGN.md) is a redirect stub only; edit the targeted doc above.

## When to update

Update docs if you touch any of:

- `csv-utils/src/**`, `csv-utils-core/src/**`
- `Cargo.toml`, `pixi.toml`, `recipe/recipe.yaml`
- `scripts/generate_test_data.py`, `scripts/capture_tui_snapshot.py`

Skip doc updates only for pure refactors with **no** behavior, CLI, TUI, or task-name changes.

## Checklist before finishing

- [ ] Relevant doc(s) describe behavior **after** your change
- [ ] [README.md](../README.md) examples still run as written
- [ ] No stale references (removed tasks, wrong paths)
- [ ] TUI keyboard/mouse tables match `csv-utils/src/tui/app.rs`

## Style

- Factual, present tense; tables for bindings and flags
- Prefer editing the section doc over duplicating content in multiple files
- Bump “Last verified against” in [docs/index.md](../docs/index.md) when materially refreshing docs
